rows.label: tlk401009_msg0001
rows.name:
The Superbian Divine Beast
battleship's defenses are solid.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0002
rows.name:
It wouldn't be easy to take it down
with any weapon in this port.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0003
rows.name:
And I hear that only a very
select group of trusted
individuals will be attending.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0004
rows.name:
Getting close enough to stab
someone would be impossible.
Assassination is out of the question.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0005
rows.name:
The atmosphere is tense,
but I'm not worried.
